episodes.title: I Joined an Eating Disorder Cult
episodes.description: This is the story of Chenelle, who found herself in the grip of an eating disorder cult—one that disguised itself as a supportive community but became a dangerous obsession.In this video, she opens up about the manipulation, the toxic mindset, and the struggle to break free. From the darkest moments to the fight for recovery, this is a raw, honest account of survival, healing, and hope.Chenelle's Links: https://www.nationaleatingdisorders.o... https://substack.com/@chenelledghoshal If you have a unique story you'd like to share on the podcast, please fill out this form: https://forms.gle/ZiHgdoK4PLRAddiB9 or send an email to wereallinsanepodcast@gmail.com Business Inquiries please contact: weareallinsane@outloudtalent.com
